
A tool for performance optimization on Heterogeneous Systems using workload distribution and 
Performance functions.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

The following packages are required for compilation:
1. cmake
2. Doxygen

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

To build and install:

1). cd <HPOPT root directory>

Replace '<HPOPT root directory>' by the directory where HPOPT is downloaded.

2). mkdir build
3). cd build
4). cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<HPOPT Installation Directory> ..

Replace '<HPOPT Installation Directory>' by the directory where
HetDist installation files (libraries, binaries) should be placed.

5). make
6). make doc
7). make install

